{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.1","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:1","prev_osis_id":"Prov.014.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.002,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    Une r\u00e9ponse douce calme la fureur,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais une parole dure excite la col\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.2","name":"Proverbes 15:2","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.14.35","name":"Proverbes 14:35","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.14.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.2","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:2","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>La langue des sages rend la science aimable,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Et la bouche des insens\u00e9s r\u00e9pand la folie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.3","name":"Proverbes 15:3","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.1","name":"Proverbes 15:1","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.3","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:3","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>\n    Les yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel sont en tout lieu,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Observant les m\u00e9chants et les bons.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.4","name":"Proverbes 15:4","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.2","name":"Proverbes 15:2","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.4","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:4","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>\n    La langue douce est un arbre de vie,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais la langue perverse brise l\u2019\u00e2me.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.5","name":"Proverbes 15:5","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.3","name":"Proverbes 15:3","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.5","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:5","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>L\u2019insens\u00e9 d\u00e9daigne l\u2019instruction de son p\u00e8re,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais celui qui a \u00e9gard \u00e0 la r\u00e9primande agit avec prudence.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.6","name":"Proverbes 15:6","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.4","name":"Proverbes 15:4","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.6","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:6","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Il y a grande abondance dans la maison du juste,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais il y a du trouble dans les profits du m\u00e9chant.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.7","name":"Proverbes 15:7","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.5","name":"Proverbes 15:5","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.7","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:7","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Les l\u00e8vres des sages r\u00e9pandent la science,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais le c\u0153ur des insens\u00e9s n\u2019est pas droit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.8","name":"Proverbes 15:8","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.6","name":"Proverbes 15:6","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.8","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:8","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>\n    Le sacrifice des m\u00e9chants est en horreur \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais la pri\u00e8re des hommes droits lui est agr\u00e9able.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.9","name":"Proverbes 15:9","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.7","name":"Proverbes 15:7","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.9","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:9","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>La voie du m\u00e9chant est en horreur \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais il aime celui qui poursuit la justice.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.10","name":"Proverbes 15:10","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.8","name":"Proverbes 15:8","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.10","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:10","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Une correction s\u00e9v\u00e8re menace celui qui abandonne le sentier;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Celui qui hait la r\u00e9primande mourra.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.11","name":"Proverbes 15:11","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.9","name":"Proverbes 15:9","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.11","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:11","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>\n    Le s\u00e9jour des morts et l\u2019ab\u00eeme sont devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Combien plus les c\u0153urs des fils de l\u2019homme!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.12","name":"Proverbes 15:12","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.10","name":"Proverbes 15:10","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.12","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:12","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Le moqueur n\u2019aime pas qu\u2019on le reprenne,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il ne va point vers les sages.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.13","name":"Proverbes 15:13","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.11","name":"Proverbes 15:11","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.13","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:13","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>\n    Un c\u0153ur joyeux rend le visage serein;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais quand le c\u0153ur est triste, l\u2019esprit est abattu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.14","name":"Proverbes 15:14","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.12","name":"Proverbes 15:12","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.14","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:14","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Un c\u0153ur intelligent cherche la science,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais la bouche des insens\u00e9s se pla\u00eet \u00e0 la folie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.15","name":"Proverbes 15:15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.13","name":"Proverbes 15:13","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.15","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:15","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Tous les jours du malheureux sont mauvais,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais le c\u0153ur content est un festin perp\u00e9tuel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.16","name":"Proverbes 15:16","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.14","name":"Proverbes 15:14","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.16","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:16","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>\n    Mieux vaut peu, avec la crainte de l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Qu\u2019un grand tr\u00e9sor, avec le trouble.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.17","name":"Proverbes 15:17","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.15","name":"Proverbes 15:15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.17","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:17","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>\n    Mieux vaut de l\u2019herbe pour nourriture, l\u00e0 o\u00f9 r\u00e8gne l\u2019amour,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Qu\u2019un b\u0153uf engraiss\u00e9, si la haine est l\u00e0.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.18","name":"Proverbes 15:18","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.16","name":"Proverbes 15:16","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.18","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:18","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>\n    Un homme violent excite des querelles,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais celui qui est lent \u00e0 la col\u00e8re apaise les disputes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.19","name":"Proverbes 15:19","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.17","name":"Proverbes 15:17","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.19","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:19","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Le chemin du paresseux est comme une haie d\u2019\u00e9pines,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais le sentier des hommes droits est aplani.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.20","name":"Proverbes 15:20","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.18","name":"Proverbes 15:18","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.20","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:20","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>\n    Un fils sage fait la joie de son p\u00e8re,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et un homme insens\u00e9 m\u00e9prise sa m\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.21","name":"Proverbes 15:21","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.19","name":"Proverbes 15:19","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.21","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:21","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>\n    La folie est une joie pour celui qui est d\u00e9pourvu de sens,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais un homme intelligent va le droit chemin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.22","name":"Proverbes 15:22","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.20","name":"Proverbes 15:20","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.22","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:22","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>\n    Les projets \u00e9chouent, faute d\u2019une assembl\u00e9e qui d\u00e9lib\u00e8re;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais ils r\u00e9ussissent quand il y a de nombreux conseillers.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.23","name":"Proverbes 15:23","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.21","name":"Proverbes 15:21","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.23","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:23","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>On \u00e9prouve de la joie \u00e0 donner une r\u00e9ponse de sa bouche;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et combien est agr\u00e9able une parole dite \u00e0 propos!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.24","name":"Proverbes 15:24","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.22","name":"Proverbes 15:22","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.24","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:24","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Pour le sage, le sentier de la vie m\u00e8ne en haut,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Afin qu\u2019il se d\u00e9tourne du s\u00e9jour des morts qui est en bas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.25","name":"Proverbes 15:25","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.23","name":"Proverbes 15:23","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.25","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:25","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>\n    L\u2019\u00c9ternel renverse la maison des orgueilleux,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais il affermit les bornes de la veuve.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.26","name":"Proverbes 15:26","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.24","name":"Proverbes 15:24","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.26","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:26","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>\n    Les pens\u00e9es mauvaises sont en horreur \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais les paroles agr\u00e9ables sont pures \u00e0 ses yeux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.27","name":"Proverbes 15:27","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.25","name":"Proverbes 15:25","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.27","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:27","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>\n    Celui qui est avide de gain trouble sa maison,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais celui qui hait les pr\u00e9sents vivra.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.28","name":"Proverbes 15:28","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.26","name":"Proverbes 15:26","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.28","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:28","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Le c\u0153ur du juste m\u00e9dite pour r\u00e9pondre,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais la bouche des m\u00e9chants r\u00e9pand des m\u00e9chancet\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.29","name":"Proverbes 15:29","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.27","name":"Proverbes 15:27","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.29","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:29","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel s\u2019\u00e9loigne des m\u00e9chants,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Mais il \u00e9coute la pri\u00e8re des justes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.30","name":"Proverbes 15:30","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.28","name":"Proverbes 15:28","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.30","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:30","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Ce qui pla\u00eet aux yeux r\u00e9jouit le c\u0153ur;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Une bonne nouvelle fortifie les membres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.31","name":"Proverbes 15:31","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.29","name":"Proverbes 15:29","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.31","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:31","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>L\u2019oreille attentive aux r\u00e9primandes qui m\u00e8nent \u00e0 la vie<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Fait son s\u00e9jour au milieu des sages.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.32","name":"Proverbes 15:32","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.30","name":"Proverbes 15:30","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.32","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:32","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.015.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Celui qui rejette la correction m\u00e9prise son \u00e2me,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Mais celui qui \u00e9coute la r\u00e9primande acquiert l\u2019intelligence.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.33","name":"Proverbes 15:33","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.31","name":"Proverbes 15:31","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.33","label":"","reference":"Proverbes 15:33","prev_osis_id":"Prov.015.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Prov.016.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Prov.15.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>\n    La crainte de l\u2019\u00c9ternel enseigne la sagesse,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Et l\u2019humilit\u00e9 pr\u00e9c\u00e8de la gloire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Prov.15","name":"Proverbes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.16.1","name":"Proverbes 16:1","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.16.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Prov.15.32","name":"Proverbes 15:32","id":"fra-LSG:Prov.15.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocum